Hey Gijigalakama Rakaa Lakama
Gijigalakama Rakaa

Generation To Generationu
Mugi Beeltaar Egga Mugga

Nera Nudile Helteen Kelanna

Hey Gijigalakama Rakaa Lakama
Gijigalakama Rakaa
Lights On Andare Lit Aag Battaare
Blockbusterrr Pakka

Generation To Generationu
Mugi Beeltaar Egga Mugga
Aye Chinna Oy Chinna
Forever Record Breaks

Cut-Out Andre Naan Antaare
Daulat Ella‚Ä¶ No Chance

Yaariginta Naaven Kammi
Anta Aagu‚Ä¶ Advance

Ille Hutti Ille Beledu Niyattaagi Ille Duddu
Oorudhdhaara Maadovr Naavu Pakka Localsu!

Yeshte Saahukaara Idru Oorigoore Kondkondidru
Nanna Preetsovr Maatra Nange Celebritiesu

Yene Aagogli
Cho-Ninna Bidovr Naavalla

Beda Namage Berevr Kathe Puraana

Oyy
Cho-Yenappa

Nimge Yashassu

Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek!!

snippet.title: Alice In Borderland Season 3 | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
The survival action series "Alice in Borderland" became the most watched Japanese Netflix title by worldwide audiences.

Now, the "games" that took the world by storm begin once again.

In the previous season, Arisu (#KentoYamazaki) and Usagi (#TaoTsuchiya) cleared all of the games and returned to the real world. They have since gotten married and established a happy life together. Their memories of the borderland were erased, but they see glimpses of it in dreams and hallucinations. One day, Usagi, led by afterlife researcher Ryuji (#KentoKaku), suddenly vanishes. At the same time as Usagi's disappearance, Banda (#HayatoIsomura) hands Arisu the final card: the Joker.

The uncharted journey led by the mysterious Joker card is about to unfold...

Season 3 of the Netflix Series "Alice in Borderland" is set for worldwide release on Thursday, September 25, 2025, only on Netflix.

#AliceinBorderlandS3, #AliceinBorderland3, #Netflix

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81682895

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Alice In Borderland Season 3 | Official Trailer | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

When a morbid professor pulls Usagi back to Borderland, Arisu goes after her. But can he survive a new round of deadly games and escape the Joker's plans?

snippet.title: Ufff Yeh Siyapaa Trailer | G.Ashok | A.R. Rahman | Sohum, Nushrratt, Nora, Omkar, Sharib | 5th Sept
snippet.description:
In this uniquely wordless comedy of errors, Kesari Lal Singh (Sohum Shah), a sheepish common man, finds himself entangled in a spiraling mess when his wife, Pushpa (Nushrratt Bharuccha), leaves him - convinced he‚Äôs been flirting with their neighbour, Kamini (Nora Fatehi). He hasn‚Äôt. But before he can clear his name, a wrongly delivered drug parcel sets off a chain of escalating disasters, the worst of which is a dead body turning up in his home. As Kesari scrambles to fix the situation, another corpse appears - turning his house into a full-blown crime scene. To make matters worse, Police Inspector Hasmukh (Omkar Kapoor) arrives with a personal agenda of his own, only adding to the madness. What follows is a wildly absurd, darkly comic chain of events - unfolding without a single spoken word.

Ufff Yeh Siyapaa releases in theatres on 5th September 2025.

Starring: Sohum Shah, Nushrratt Bharuccha, Nora Fatehi, Omkar Kapoor and Sharib Hashmi
Presented By: Luv Films
Written & Directed By: G. Ashok
Produced By: Luv Ranjan and Ankur Garg
Music By: A.R. Rahman

snippet.title: Sri Vinayaka Vratha Kadha & Pooja Vidhanam | Ganesh Chaturthi Special | Vinayaka Chavithi Songs
snippet.description:
üôè Sri Vinayaka Vratha Kadha & Pooja Vidhanam ‚Äì A divine and sacred guide to performing Vinayaka Chavithi Vratham with proper rituals, mantras, and the traditional story of Lord Ganesha.

Narrated by : Tadala Srinivas, I. Muralidhara Sharma


Celebrate this Ganesh Chaturthi with devotion and learn the correct pooja procedure (Vidhanam) along with the auspicious Vinayaka Vratha Kadha in Telugu. This video is perfect for those who wish to observe the vratam at home with sincerity and faith.

Sri Vinayaka Vratha Kadha is a central part of the Vinayaka Vratham Telugu tradition, observed with deep devotion during VinayakaChavithi. On this auspicious day, devotees perform the Vinayaka Pooja Vidhanam Telugu, carefully following each of the Vinayaka Pooja Steps as outlined in the Ganesh Chaturthi Pooja Procedure.

The atmosphere is filled with devotion as families come together, guided by the Vinayaka Vratha Pooja Guide, to offer prayers and perform rituals. The celebration is further enhanced by spiritual music, including Vinayaka Chavithi Songs, Ganesh Chaturthi Special Songs, and uplifting Lord Ganesha Devotional Songs.

Songs like Vinayaka Aarti Telugu, Ganesh Bhakti Songs Telugu, and the latest Vinayaka Chavithi 2025 Telugu Songs add a divine rhythm to the puja. This GaneshChaturthiSpecial becomes even more meaningful when observed with heartfelt devotion, traditional GaneshChaturthiPooja, and the blessings of Lord Ganesha.

‚úî Complete Vinayaka Chavithi Pooja Vidhanam
‚úî Sri Vinayaka Vratha Kadha in Telugu
‚úî Ideal for Ganesh Chaturthi festival celebrations

‚ú® Chant, pray, and invite Lord Vinayaka‚Äôs blessings for prosperity, wisdom, and happiness.

Presenting ‚ÄúSabhi Khaas‚Äù ‚Äì the 2025 Haryanvi Hip Hop Anthem by Sumit Parta. 
Raw bars. Street energy. Real talk. 
This track hits hard with loyalty, betrayal & brotherhood stories straight from Haryana‚Äôs rap scene.

With powerful lyrics, heavy delivery, and authentic street-style flow, Sumit Parta turns real-life struggles into a bold hip hop statement. Sabhi Khaas is more than just a song ‚Äî it‚Äôs a reality check on friendship, fake loyalty, and survival.

Blending smooth Haryanvi lyrics with a pan-India rap appeal, this track connects with anyone who knows the grind. If you‚Äôre looking for authentic Haryanvi hip hop, Sabhi Khaas is your soundtrack.

Hard Bars. Real Emotions. Pure Haryana Vibes.
